  "text": "The molecular function and biological process enrichment of the transcript were analyzed using GlueGo [CITATION_1] ). The molecular pathway enrichment of candidate genes were analyzed through GSEA [CITATION_2] . If a p-value was ≤ 0.05, the term was deemed as statistically significant. Moreover, Metscape was also used to analyze the integrated pathways of genes and metabonomic data [CITATION_3] .",
